divs: Sighting DetailsMe and my 3 friends were standing in front of the Safeway store, at around 6:20pm and we all saw the circular object above the clouds, it hovered around 3 minutes, then split apart, and started blinking, then disappeared. I have a picture of it as well.
trends: There have been 2 other sightings in New River
There were no other sightings in New River on or around September 1st 2012
Summary: circular object above the clouds (daylight), hovering, it split apart and started blinking, then it disappeared
